# External Uptime Monitor

External site monitoring using GitHub Actions + Telegram Bot.

Checks site health every 5 minutes from GitHub servers. Alerts via Telegram when site goes DOWN or recovers.

## Setup

See [README.md](README.md) for full setup instructions.

## Structure

```
.github/workflows/uptime-check.yml   # GitHub Actions workflow
README.md                            # Setup guide (Vietnamese)
```
